assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Moon Environment Technology Co.,Ltd. manufactures and sells air-conditioning and refrigeration equipment in China and internationally. The company offers refrigeration equipment, which includes refrigeration compressor, condensing units, water cooled chillers, brine chiller units, and marine refrigeration compressor units; food processing equipment, such as food quick freezing device, industrial food dryer machines, vacuum fryer machine lines, and fresh food processing machine lines; and auxiliary refrigeration equipment, comprising evaporative condensers and A2 refrigerated tanks. It also provides various industrial air coolers, cold storage panels, such as EPS insulated, metal corrugated, and polyurethane sandwich panels; flake and block ice making machines; air conditioning equipment that includes water cooled centrifugal and screw chillers, screw compressor water source heat pumps, modular air hanging units, air cooled screw heat pumps, and fan coil units; and gas compression equipment, which comprise screw air compressor and process gas compressor package units. In addition, the company offers industrial and commercial refrigeration system application, and environment air conditioning and refrigeration system application, as well as project planning, one stop service center, engineering design, equipment matching, logistics and transportation, installation and commissioning, equipment maintenance, technical training, follow-up services, and system improvement and upgrading services. Further, it provides services such as for overseas sale department, sales service, and spare parts. The company was formerly known as Yantai Moon Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Moon Environment Technology Co., Ltd. in September 2017. Moon Environment Technology Co.,Ltd. was founded in 1956 and is based in Yantai, China.
